  nnoremap <silent> <leader>g` :call ReviewLastCommit()<CR>

  augroup fugitiveSettings
    autocmd!
    autocmd FileType gitcommit setlocal nolist
    autocmd BufReadPost fugitive://* setlocal bufhidden=delete
  augroup END
